quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,104,"Bagambe nti: abange mmwe abantu bwe muba nga mulina okubuusabuusa mu ddiini yange (mukitegeere nti) sisinza abo be musinza nemuva ku Katonda, wabula nsinza Katonda oyo abatta ,era nnalagirwa mbeere mu bakkiriza"
  10,105,Era tereera mu ddiini ya Katonda n'goli mwesimbu era ddala tobeeranga mu bagatta e bintu e birala ku Katonda
  10,106,Tolekanga Katonda n'osaba e kintu e kirala ekyo ekitakugasa era ekitayinza kukutuusako kabi naye bwonookikola mazima ddala ggwe olwo nno onoobeera mu abo abeeyisa obubi
  10,107,"Singa Mukama Katonda akutuusaako ekibi tewali ayinza kukikuggyako okugyako yye, ate singa aba akwagalizza kirungi teri ayinza kuzzaayo birungibye, abifunyisa oyo gwaba ayagadde mu baddube, era yye bulijjo ye musonyiyi, omusaasizi owa nnamaddala"
  10,108,"Bagambe (Ggwe Muhammad) nti; abange mmwe abantu amazima gabajjidde okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe oyo yenna alungama aba yeelungamidde, ate oyo abula okubulakwe kukosa yye. Nze siri mukuumi ku mmwe"
  10,109,"Era goberera ebyo ebitumwa gyoli era ogumiikirize okutuusa Katonda lwa naasalawo, anti bulijjo yye yaasinga abasalawo bonna"